        "action": "Ban the sale of needle and syringe sets to individuals without a prescription.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "As current regulations stand, anyone can order needle and syringe sets online, without proving their intentions.\r\nThe recent outbreak of \u201cspiking by injection\u201d cannot be helped by the ease of acquiring these sets. Needles should be prescribed with medication, and not as a separate transaction.",
